Issue :{" "} High Volume of patients seeking doctors for common ailments like cold, fever and viral infections and a scarcity of Healthcare professional compared to patient load leads to bottleneck and inefficiency.

Solution :{" "} MedAI is a Medicine Recommendation System Developed to eliminate the bottleneck and improve the efficiency in treatments by automating the medicine prescription service for various common diseases which include Common Cold , Fever , Stomach Pain , Acne & so on. The System leverages the use of Knowledge Graphs , Large Language Models to give reliable and accurate prescriptions to the patients based on the symptoms and the interaction with the patient. This system greatly reduces hospital bottlenecks, increasing efficiency manifold. Doctors could then concentrate on more challenging cases, leading to improved overall efficiency for patients and healthcare institutions alike.

Chat with our System{" "} - Type in your symptoms to get the Medicine Recommendation and you are free to ask more about the medicine such as its price, TypeOfSell , Salts_Used , How_to_Use , How_it_Works , Side_effects & Alternate Medicines.

Recommendation Provided by the System are :

Robust

  • Reliable
  • Accurate
